flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Scheduled S&OP/IBP meeting kickoff.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawler - Retrieve demand plan data from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Analyze demand plan data using Cortex Auto Forecast.]
  N2 --> N3[UI: UI Screens - Present demand plan and gather executive feedback.]
  N3 --> N4[Stream: DDM/Crawler - Retrieve supply plan scenarios from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N4 --> N5[Cortex: AutoML - Analyze supply plan scenarios using AutoML.]
  N5 --> N6[UI: UI Screens - Present supply plan scenarios and gather executive feedback.]
  N6 --> N7[Stream: DDM/Crawler - Retrieve financial implications from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N7 --> N8[Cortex: Cortex Monitoring - Analyze financial implications using Cortex Monitoring.]
  N8 --> N9[UI: UI Screens - Present financial implications and gather executive approval.]
  N9 --> N10{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Facilitate strategic trade-off decisions.}
  N10 -->|Primary| P1[Action: Automated presentation and approval of consolidated demand and supply plans, financial alignment, and strategic trade-offs.]
  P1 --> Z1[Outcome: Improved OTIF, reduced stockouts and excess inventory, optimized EBITDA and working capital.]
  N10 -->|Insufficient data for demand plan ana...| B1[Notify stakeholders and request additional data.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Delayed decision-making until data is available.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N10 -->|Disagreement on preferred supply scen...| B2[Escalate to senior executives for final decision.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Final supply scenario selected after escalation.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N10 -->|Financial implications exceed budget ...| B3[Re-evaluate supply and demand plans to align with budget.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Adjusted plans presented for re-approval.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]